I"O<h2 id="1-재귀함수란">1. 재귀함수란?</h2>

<p>재귀함수란, 내 자신을 반복해서 호출하는 함수. <br />
예를 들면,</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"><span class="kd">func</span> <span class="nf">recursiveFunction</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="nf">recursiveFunction</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="p">}</span></code></pre></figure>

<p><br /></p>

<p>다음과 같이 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">recursiveFunction()</code> 내에서 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">recursiveFunction()</code>을 호출함. <br />
<br />
이 경우, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">recursiveFunction()</code>함수는 <strong>재귀함수</strong> 이다.<br />
<br /></p>
:ET